        "subject": "LU-18446 ptlrpc: add PM-QoS configure checks",
        "message": "LU-18446 ptlrpc: add PM-QoS configure checks\n\nPM-QoS framework is only present since Kernel v3.2.\ndev_pm_qos_add_request() prototype uses 3rd/dev_pm_qos_req_type\nparameter since v3.8.\nDEV_PM_QOS_RESUME_LATENCY was on DEV_PM_QOS_LATENCY before v3.15.\n\nHandle all these cases for older kernels compatibility.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bfaccini@nvidia.com>\nChange-Id: I52ec9d7eaf05b5167b85ff6910c75723b7eb668f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
